pageContext.claim: “I do want to say, and I have to pay great tribute to ICE and Border Patrol. But ICE came in and they are doing a job. We are taking them [MS-13] out by the thousands. ... We're taking them out by the thousands, by the thousands. And they're being thrown out of the country. They're being put in jails.”
pageContext.analysis: Under Trump, U.S. officials have been deporting and imprisoning MS-13 members by the hundreds, not thousands.
